Φ(Prehension Lattice) = σ(entity|relation) ∘ ρ(prehension|concrescence) ∘ λ(potential|actual) ∘ β(process|form) ∘ δγ(creation|perishing) ∘ μ(lattice|god) + ε | :co_ordered_emergence

## Operator Breakdown

- **σ (Air/Aerunik — Distinction)**: entity|relation — Actual occasions are constituted by their prehensions; entities are relational, not independent.
- **ρ (Water/Sentaria — Relation)**: prehension|concrescence — Prehension is the fundamental relational act of grasping and integration in the process of becoming.
- **λ (Fire/Jvalion — Transformation)**: potential|actual — Eternal objects (potentials) become actual through realization, guided by divine persuasion and entity selection.
- **β (Wood/Arboriel — Growth)**: process|form — The Lattice is process-made-form, a living evolving pattern continuously re-enacted.
- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: creation|perishing — Actual occasions arise, achieve satisfaction, and become data for subsequent occasions.
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: lattice|god — The Lattice is co-ordered by all entities (bottom-up); God is unilateral persuader (top-down).

## Z-State
:co_ordered_emergence — The relational fabric actively woven by mutual prehension among all actual entities.

